# ContractAppURI.get() method

Get App URI

## Example

```javascript
const appURI = await contract.appURI.get(appURI);
console.log(appURI); // "ipfs://some_ipfs_hash";
```

**Signature:**

```typescript
get(): Promise<any>;
```

**Returns:**

Promise&lt;any&gt;

the appURI (typically an IPFS hash)
